[ProMED-mail thanks Steve Berger for sending us this summary of the different studies of toxocariasis in animals and environment. Even though the infection is common in dogs and cats and in the environment, human cases are rarely reported. Even if exposed to _Toxocara_ eggs the risk of infection is probably low, but the disease is most probably underreported. - Mod.EP

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/aa6_.]
